title._content: House of consul and merchant Benjamin Mollén, Lysekil, Sweden

description._content: House of consul and merchant Benjamin Gabriel Mollén with the newly planted park. (Son of old Consul Johan Gabriel Mollén who founded the first bath in Lysekil.) Konsul och handelsman Benjamin Molléns hus med den nyanlagda parken. (Son till gamle konsul Johan Gabriel Mollén som grundade Lysekils första badanläggning.) Parish (socken): Lysekil Province (landskap): Bohuslän Municipality (kommun): Lysekil County (län): Västra Götaland Photograph by: Carl Curman Date: 1864 Format: Print Persistent URL: www.kms.raa.se/cocoon/bild/show-image.html?id=16001000126084 Read more about the photo database (in english): www.kms.raa.se/cocoon/bild/about.html
